list of white items


Iron Branch gold 100
increase strenght and life regeneration with some fire resist

1 to strenght
0.3 life-regen
4% fire resist

Leaf Branch gold 100
increase agility and movement speed with some poison resist

1 to agility
3 attackspeed
4% poison resist

Wisdom Branch gold 100
increase intelligence and mana regeneration with some frost resist

1 to intelligence
0.3 mana-regen
4% frost resist

Elemental Dust
increase the user life regen and mana with some pure resist also giving a chance to deal bonus damage

Passive 1 basic attack crit
chance 20%
damage 125%

